 false,\n118:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n119:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n120:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n121:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3457#issuecomment-3001996375\",\n122:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n123:     }\n124:   ],\n125:   \"title\": \"Track the addition of VCCF vasculature terms here\",\n126:   \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3457\"\n127: }\n\n(End of file - total 127 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"body\": \"### Preferred term labels, synonyms, suggested definitions, references, parent terms\\n* The targeted terms and their labels, synonyms come from [this table.](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1QrXvmsiCPqFQy6ZMHJQiE2rySrhmbQ1TE7GgDsg9ZFk/edit?gid=695544266#gid=695544266)\\n\\n### Priority organs\\n\\n```tsv\\n1.\\t eye\\n2.\\t heart\\n3.\\t kidney\\n4.\\t large intestine\\n5.\\t liver\\n6.\\t lung\\n7.\\t pancreas\\n8.\\t skin of body\\n9.\\t small intestine\\n10.\\t spleen \\n```\\n\\n### Remain be added\\n* as of [2024-12-24](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1zvY1smk9FvhPorn3raqQss7nYkEFQOOSfVGmBbwiLdQ/edit?gid=2125289498#gid=2125289498): **659**.\\n* as of [2025-01-09](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1zvY1smk9FvhPorn3raqQss7nYkEFQOOSfVGmBbwiLdQ/edit?gid=2125289498#gid=2125289498): **586**.\\n* as of [2025-01-27](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1zvY1smk9FvhPorn3raqQss7nYkEFQOOSfVGmBbwiLdQ/edit?gid=2125289498#gid=2125289498): **568**.\\n\\n\\n\\n\",\n  \"comments\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAAidd86Yqm1_\",\n      \"author\": {\n        \"login\": \"rays22\"\n      },\n      \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n      \"body\": \"### Mapping table of *380 vccf terms* that already exist in Uberon\\r\\n* as of [2024-12-24](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1zvY1smk9FvhPorn3raqQss7nYkEFQOOSfVGmBbwiLdQ/edit?gid=92781377#gid=92781377)\\r\\n\\r\\ndefined_class | label | mapping predicate | Uberon ID | Uberon_label\\r\\n-- | -- | -- | -- | --\\r\\nVCCF:1000493 | anterior humeral circumflex artery | skos:exactMatch | UBERON:8600106 | anterior humeral circumflex artery\\r\\nVCCF:1000792 | lumbar vein | skos:exactMatch | UBERON:8600105 | lumbar vein\\r\\nVCCF:1000794 | intervertebral vein | skos:exactMatch | UBERON:8600104 | intervertebral vein\\r\\nVCCF:1000641 | left anterior descending artery | skos:exactMatch | UBERON:8600102 | left anterior descending artery\\r\\nVCCF:1000055 | descending palatine artery | skos:exactMatch | UBERON:8600101 | descending palatine artery\\r\\nVCCF:1000052 | artery of pterygoid canal | skos:exactMatch | UBERON:8600100 | artery of pterygoid canal\\r\\nVCCF:1000048 | accessory meningeal artery | skos:exactMatch | UBERON:8600099 | accessory meningeal artery\\r\\nVCCF:1000045 | dorsal lingual artery | skos:exactMatch | UBERON:8600098 | dorsal lingual artery\\r\\nVCCF:1000044 | deep lingual artery | skos:exactMatch | UBERON:8600097 | deep lingual artery\\r\\nVCCF:1000040 | submental artery | skos:exactMatch | UBERON:8600096 | submental artery\\r\\nVCCF:1000036 | ascending palatine artery | skos:exactMatch | UBERON:8600095 | ascending palatine artery\\r\\nVCCF:1001020 | intra-acinar arteriole | skos:exactMatch | UBERON:8600094 | intra-acinar arteriole\\r\\nVCCF:1000966 | ulnar vein | skos:exactMatch | UBERON:8600093 | ulnar vein\\r\\nVCCF:1000964 | radial vein | skos:exactMatch | UBERON:8600092 | radial vein\\r\\nVCCF:1000931 | inferior anastomotic vein | skos:exactMatch | UBERON:8600091 | inferior anastomotic vein\\r\\nVCCF:1000896 | hypophyseal vein | skos:exactMatch | UBERON:8600090 | hypophyseal vein\\r\\nVCCF:1000884 | transverse nasal root vein | skos:exactMatch | UBERON:8600089 | transver... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n      \"createdAt\": \"2024-12-24T17:25:35Z\",\n      \"includesCreatedEdit\": true,\n      \"isMinimized\": false,\n      \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n      \"reactionGroups\": [],\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/obophenotype/uberon/issues/3457#issuecomment-2561305983\",\n      \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAAidd86Z1p6u\",","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"__issue_context__.json","time":{"start":1778979834652,"end":1778979834731}},"id":"prt_e33760b0f0014E6Dg2zwk2qQsn","sessionID":"ses_1cc8a3441ffeZxrqvOd4ujym81","messageID":"msg_e3375f729001IQYSY8zVG2tQZt"}}
